local Tool = script.Parent;
enabled = true
local colors = {Color3.new(1,0,0), Color3.new(0,1,0), Color3.new(0,0,1), Color3.new(1,.5,0), Color3.new(0,.5,1)}
function onActivated() if not enabled then return end
enabled = false
local spark = Tool.Handle:FindFirstChild("Sparkle") if (spark == nil) then local spark = Instance.new("Sparkles")
spark.Color = colors[math.random(1,#colors)] spark.Name = "Sparkle" spark.Parent = Tool.Handle Tool.Handle.DrinkSound.Looped = true Tool.Handle.DrinkSound:Play()
else spark:Remove() Tool.Handle.DrinkSound.Looped = false Tool.Handle.DrinkSound:Stop() end
wait(1)
enabled = true
end
function onEquipped() Tool.Handle.OpenSound:play() end
script.Parent.Activated:connect(onActivated) script.Parent.Equipped:connect(onEquipped)
